4. cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper discusses the power allocation for transmissions in the source-to-relay and relay-to-destination phases, which is a topic related to systems and control. 
5. cs.MA (Multiagent Systems): The paper discusses the design and deployment of backscatter nodes, which can be considered as a topic related to multiagent systems.
